@startuml jkahn117_aws-news

participant "RSS Feed" as RSS
participant "EventBridge" as EB
participant "Ingestion Lambda" as IL
participant "S3" as S3
participant "DynamoDB" as DDB
participant "Image Processing Lambda" as IPL
participant "ElastiCache" as EC
participant "AppSync API" as API
participant "CloudFront" as CF
participant "Next.js Frontend" as FE
participant "Pinpoint" as PP
participant "Kinesis Firehose" as KF

RSS -> IL: Fetch RSS feed
IL -> S3: Store article content
IL -> DDB: Store article metadata
IL -> EB: Publish article_created event
EB -> IPL: Trigger image processing
IPL -> S3: Process and store images
IPL -> DDB: Update article metadata
FE -> CF: Request content
CF -> API: Forward request
API -> EC: Check cache
EC --> API: Return cached data (if available)
API -> DDB: Query data (if not in cache)
DDB --> API: Return data
API -> EC: Update cache
API --> CF: Return data
CF --> FE: Serve content
FE -> PP: Send user interaction data
PP -> KF: Stream analytics data
KF -> S3: Store analytics data

@enduml